    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Digital inkjet prints that use pigment-based ink rather than dye-based ink to create an image. These are often additionally created with high-quality fine art papers or other media as substrates for longevity and are considered archival.</Note_Text>
